  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe through some-- you know, you know, through-- they went to, maybe, to the Polish-- what they called the Polish--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POLISH], what they call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish mayor and they asked him who is between the Jews which, which we should appoint to be a Judenrat?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they must have told them, hey, they are the well-known Jews from a nice family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they did, they asked right away for some, some young people to, to, to supply young people to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what did the Judenrat do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Judenrat picked up some young people, the age of between 15 and 20.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wouldn't, you know, send some people which are, let's say, a little bit older or married or something to, to go to do manual work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the beginning of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we used to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the Germans were occupying us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a lot of German-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do they call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The police and Gestapo, which they occupied in Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also, which they-- what they, they call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm, I'm thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, in the interview, it's kind of hard to, to, to, to explain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a border patrol.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a border patrol, which they, you know, they, they-- we had a border, like I just mentioned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were a lot of patrol-- German [? patrol. ?] And we worked for him, like cleaning cars and cleaning their houses and shoveling snow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was manual work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
